{"municipality":"宗像市","pref":"福岡県","muni_code":"402206","count":33,"items":[{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"鎮国寺本堂","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"建造物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1974-03-30","location":"鎮国寺","description":"慶安3年(1650)建立。五仏堂とも言われ、宗像氏が五社の本地仏を安置したと『宗像記』に記される。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0002"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"平山天満宮本殿","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"建造物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2013-05-22","location":"平山天満宮","description":"天保14年(1843)の建築と推定され、覆屋が必須の板葺神社本殿は18世紀末以前の宗像地域の社殿建築形式の特色。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0028"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"長福寺（長宝寺）観音堂","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"建造物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1991-02-27","location":"八所神社長宝観音堂","description":"18世紀中頃以前の建築で観音堂禅宗様式の形式を有する。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0016"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"八所宮本殿及び拝殿","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"建造物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2016-10-14","location":"八所宮","description":"本殿は三間社流造で宝永6年(1709)の建築。拝殿は江戸時代中期の典型的神社建築として高い価値を有する。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0029"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"黒田二十四騎久野家隊列図","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"絵画","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1987-04-17","location":"海の道むなかた館","description":"江戸時代末期の安藤菊作作。福岡藩の軍制の記録としても貴重。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0012"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"千手観音立像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1987-04-17","location":"梅谷寺","description":"背部に正安3年(1301)の紀年銘のほか、仏師名などが記される。ヒノキ材一木造。高さ123.5cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0010"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"用山の阿弥陀如来坐像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1988-10-12","location":"用山観音堂","description":"11世紀頃の作と考えられている。クス材を用い一木で割った後、割矧造りとしたもの。高さ128.5cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0014"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"木造不動明王像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1991-11-20","location":"八所神社長宝寺観音堂","description":"平安後期の作。クス材を用い、一木から割矧技法で造られる。高さ203.5cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0017"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"木造天王像　甲・乙","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1991-11-20","location":"八所神社長宝寺観音堂","description":"鎌倉時代の作で平安時代以来の伝統的な直立する天王像の形状を継承する。クス材一木造。甲は高さ106.5cm、乙は高さ116.0cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0020"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"木造大威徳明王像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1991-11-20","location":"八所神社長宝寺観音堂","description":"鎌倉時代の作で像容の基本は整い威容をとどめる。クス材一木造。高さ120.2cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0018"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"木造大日如来像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1991-11-20","location":"久戸区大日堂","description":"平安時代の作。ヒノキ材を用い古風な技法で造る。平安仏のなかでも原状をよく残す。高さ61.7cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0019"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"平山の阿弥陀如来立像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2001-06-01","location":"平山区大師堂","description":"平安時代後期の作で、ヒノキ材を用い一木から割別技法で造る。高さ95.7cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0025"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"平山の天部形立像","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"彫刻","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2001-06-01","location":"平山区大師堂","description":"平安時代後期の作で、ヒノキ材を用いた寄木技法で造る。高さ93.8cm。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0024"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"承福寺文書","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"書跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1974-10-19","location":"承福寺","description":"宗像氏家臣・占部安延の建立といわれる承福寺には、江戸時代の福岡藩に関わる黒田孝高や長政らの公書が残る。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0003"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"増福院文書","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"書跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1987-04-17","location":"増福院","description":"増福院は天文年間末期(1550)頃の建立とされ、本資料は中世末期の宗像地域を知る上で貴重。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0011"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"平信盛笠塔婆","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"考古資料","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1974-03-30","location":"宗像市池田","description":"宗像地方に伝わる平家落人の墓とも足跡をしのぶ墓碑。落人の由来や子孫の足跡などが記される。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0001"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"大図（土地字図）","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"歴史資料","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2004-03-25","location":"海の道むなかた館","description":"明治時代以降の地籍を知るうえで貴重な字図。福岡県下に同様の資料は無い。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0026"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"王丸八幡神社棟札","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"歴史資料","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2017-08-17","location":"海の道むなかた館","description":"中世〜近代までの一連の棟札。中世以来の造営・修復の経緯が継続的に分かる資料。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0032"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"王丸八幡神社宮座行事関係資料","category":"民俗文化財","subcategory":"有形民俗文化財","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2017-08-17","location":"海の道むなかた館","description":"江戸時代〜現在の宮座行事の内容・変遷が分かる貴重な資料。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0031"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"主基地方風俗舞","category":"民俗文化財","subcategory":"無形民俗文化財","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1978-07-12","location":"宗像大社","description":"主基地方風俗舞として我が国で現存する唯一の神楽舞。宗像大社春・秋大祭で、雅楽と風俗歌にあわせ4人の青年男子が舞って神前に奉納する。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0008"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"神湊盆踊り","category":"民俗文化財","subcategory":"無形民俗文化財","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1990-03-31","location":"神湊盆踊保存会","description":"地方まわりの旅役者が教えたとも、上方の商船が村の若者に教えたともいわれる。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0015"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"宗像大社みあれ祭","category":"民俗文化財","subcategory":"無形民俗文化財","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2017-08-08","location":"宗像大社海洋神事奉賛会","description":"中世の祭事を参考に考案された祭り。宗像七浦の協力で100艘以上の船が集まる壮大な海上神幸が有名。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0030"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"八所宮神幸行事","category":"民俗文化財","subcategory":"無形民俗文化財","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2018-09-28","location":"吉武地区歴史・伝統文化保存振興会","description":"江戸時代の資料に記された当時の神幸の形を良好に残す地区の歴史と伝統を強く継承する稀有な行事。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0033"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"鐘崎（上八）貝塚","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1987-02-01","location":"宗像市上八","description":"海浜の砂丘上にある縄文時代後期の遺跡。縄文時代後期（約4〜3千年前）の標式土器「鐘崎式土器」が出土。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0009"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"久原澤田古墳群","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1988-10-12","location":"宗像ユリックス","description":"4〜7世紀に築造された古墳群で、前方後円墳1基と円墳3基を復元整備。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0013"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"朝町竹重遺跡","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1992-06-30","location":"宗像市朝町","description":"弥生時代の土壙・木棺墓群、古墳時代の円墳群を検出。弥生時代の鏡、銅斧、銅矛などの遺物が出土。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0021"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"宗像氏貞の墓地及び石塔","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1993-03-31","location":"承福寺","description":"最後の宗像大宮司・氏貞の墓所。天正14年(1586)に嵩ヶ嶽城で死去し、家臣・占部氏が埋葬したといわれる。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0022"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"平等寺瀬戸遺跡","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1993-04-15","location":"宗像市平等寺","description":"6世紀後半の円墳2基と小型石室5基を調査、うち円墳1基の石室内から大形馬鈴、金銅装の鞆尻などが出土。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0023"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"田野瀬戸古墳","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"2006-03-31","location":"宗像市田野","description":"6世紀前半頃に築造された海人集団統率者の墓と目される前方後円墳。胡籙・挂甲小札・馬具などが出土。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0027"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"田島氏八満神社境内大楠","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"天然記念物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1974-10-19","location":"氏八満神社","description":"胸高周囲6m、樹高35mを測る。樹齢は250年と推定される。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0004"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"浄光寺藤の木","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"天然記念物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1975-08-28","location":"浄光寺","description":"胸高周囲1m、根廻り1.5m。第31世住職三好光含の植樹で樹齢百数十年。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0007"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"依岳神社バクチの木","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"天然記念物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1975-08-28","location":"依岳神社","description":"バラ科の常緑高木で桜と同属。バクチで身をくるみはがされるように部分的に絶えず剥がれ落ちることからこの名がある。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0006"},{"pref":"福岡県","municipality":"宗像市","name":"いちょうの木","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"天然記念物","designation":"市指定","designated_date":"1975-08-28","location":"依岳神社","description":"いちょうは中国原産とされるがかなり古くから日本に植生する。6月に開花し10月に結実する。","source_url":"https://www.city.munakata.lg.jp/kiji0038944/3_8944_7261_up_mi4tzbcm.pdf","source_format":"pdf","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","jmh_id":"JMH-402206-0005"}]}